FBIS3-60847 "jptot001__l94095" JPRS-TOT-94-001-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 January 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Four Caucasians Kidnap Children; No Motive Given Helicopter Heads for Mineralnyye Vody LD2412004893 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0024 GM 24 Dec 93 LD2412004893 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Viktor Zhilyakov] [Text] Krasnodar, 24 Dec -- The helicopter carrying the terrorists and the hostages seized in Rostov-on-Don has just lifted off from a Krasnodar military aerodrome. It circled Krasnodar several times and took a course towards Mineralnyye Vody. One hopes that the schoolchildren who were taken hostage are safe and sound. The bandits have still not been identified.
